The paper deals with instance segmentation, which is a computer vision problem, hence cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a model that combines object detection and semantic segmentation, which involves the use of machine learning techniques, making cs.AI and cs.LG likely sub-categories as well. The paper also mentions the use of recent successful methods from both segmentation and detection, which could fall under the sub-categories of cs.CL and cs.MM.
